{"tid":370572,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"會令情侶受苦已是愛 但我答應我永不要重複犯錯","createTime":"2017-08-23T06:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T18:28:02.000Z","uid":12980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03a9795d06c8c58de86be4065017fc2c01f3a970","tid":370572,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"回味過去每一吻<br />\n真切得 於嘴邊掠過<br />\n你的內心竟在避我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經歷左咁多先發現大家最愛個個係大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果再有一次比大家<br />\n相信我會更加珍惜你,唔會再做啲野令你冇安全感<br />\n我願意比哂100%時間落你度,為左你我幾傻都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好將我地關係變做遺憾好嗎？<br />\n否則我地都會後悔一世架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee805b5802510d1c0769463fc2d8f5a7d9d033de","tid":370572,"uid":6663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"得個講字有撚用 走左先識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca58332b9c37487c38c6ff53954323430cac5e1f","tid":370572,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得個講字有撚用 走左先識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯比機會,我咪證明比佢睇佢冇揀錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇既 咁唯有放棄架啦"}]}